author: seanfinan
msg: Glorified Grep.  Tiny pipeline that simply looks up Terms based upon umls dictionary, sentence breaks and part of speech.
It can process 50,000 notes per hour on my circa-vista laptop, reading and writing to file.
LVG is commented out.  Depending upon the phase of the moon, this can add a small or large amount of time the the run.  Including LVG will enable more term recognition.
Negation, Uncertainty, etc. are commented out.
If you want to run any other modules in a pipeline then use another ae as a template.

author: arkurth
msg: Updated utils.pm::get_management_node_requests to retrieve the timestamp of the most recent changelog entry which has remoteIP set.
Updated utils.pm::changetime to compare reservation.lastcheck to changelog.timestamp if the state is inuse. If the changelog entry is newer, 'poll' is returned.
Updated get_management_node_requests to return a hash reference and updated vcld accordingly.
